/// Roles" as a brand promise. Adding or removing a value here without updating
/// the marketing draft creates drift between what we promise and what the
/// product actually does. Surfaced by /graphify on 2026-05-12 as a
/// semantically_similar_to edge linking this enum to the marketing draft.
